data.description: Beautiful home centrally located in Rio Rico, sited on a .42 acre lot.   As you come into this pleasantly inviting home you will enjoy the open feel and spacious areas of the main living room, kitchen, and formal dining area.  The ample kitchen has plenty of cabinetry, and granite countertops, and is upgraded with stainless steel appliances.  The living room includes an inviting wood-burning fireplace.  The spacious bedrooms include tile floors.   The rear yard has been fenced around the perimeter of the property for privacy and outdoor relaxation. It has mature trees, a built-in BBQ area, and a large cement pad that could be used as a basketball court area.   Enjoy the courtyard outdoors while sitting and listening to the peaceful flow of the waterfall fountain included.  *more Loaded with character, charm, and additional upgraded amenities featuring north/south orientation, tile roof,  energy efficient dual pane windows, ceiling fans, washer and dryer, and more.   Convenient location close to the supermarket, and restaurants, and it's easily accessible to the interstate.  Come view for yourself this beautiful move-in ready home!
